                                "stop": 9.443,
                                "byte_start": 28672,
                                "byte_stop": 66497,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in Number 86-1034, Virginia versus American Booksellers Association will be announced by Justice Brennan."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 9.443,
                        "stop": 185,
                        "byte_start": 66497,
